Definition: measuring instrument in which the echo of a pulse of microwave radiation is used to detect and locate distant objects
Synonyms: microwave_radar, radio_detection_and_ranging, radiolocation, verb, stative, radiolocate, measuring_instrument, measuring, instrument, in, which, the, echo, of, a, pulse, microwave, radiation, is, used, to, detect, and, locate, distant, objects
Category: noun.artifact
